"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Maj;<keycap>Gauche</keycap></"
"keycombo></shortcut> <guimenu>Fenêtre</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Déplacer "
"l'onglet à gauche</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3469
#, no-c-format
msgid "Move the current tab one place left in the list of tabs."
